  <entry>
    <title>【初识博客】记录一次我的博客之旅</title>
    <url>/2020/03/09/%E3%80%90%E5%88%9D%E8%AF%86%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E3%80%91%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>​        本着踩边所有坑的态度历经两天建成了自己的第一个博客，当然这是第一篇文章，可见此文章的地位非同一般。果不其然，其间遇见了各路小鬼在太岁头上动土。包括但不限于网络问题无法上传至根服务器，没有网站前端知识导致的修改代码问题…..遍历了所有办法几乎是十八般武艺全都用上…第一篇文章测试一下网站的标签功能是否正常，以及建立起一套标准的写文章到发文章的可靠路径，毕竟不是什么时间都有大把精力用在客制化主题上，博客还是主要以记录为目的的。</p>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="全局代码"><a href="#全局代码" class="headerlink" title="全局代码"></a><strong>全局代码</strong></h1><a id="more"></a>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">init</span>        <span class="comment">####安装</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">g</span>           <span class="comment">###生成</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">clean</span>       <span class="comment">###清除缓存</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">hexo</span> <span class="string">d</span>           <span class="comment">###上传</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="更改git代理"><a href="#更改git代理" class="headerlink" title="更改git代理"></a><strong>更改git代理</strong></h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">config</span> <span class="string">--global</span> <span class="string">http.proxy</span> <span class="string">http://127.0.0.1:10809</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">config</span> <span class="string">--global</span> <span class="string">https.proxy</span> <span class="string">https://127.0.0.1:10809</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="取消代理"><a href="#取消代理" class="headerlink" title="取消代理"></a><strong>取消代理</strong></h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">config</span> <span class="string">--global</span> <span class="string">--unset</span> <span class="string">http.proxy</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">config</span> <span class="string">--global</span> <span class="string">--unset</span> <span class="string">https.proxy</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="按装一个插件来同步："><a href="#按装一个插件来同步：" class="headerlink" title="按装一个插件来同步："></a><strong>按装一个插件来同步：</strong></h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">install</span> <span class="string">hexo-deployer-git</span> <span class="string">--save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="git-yilia主题"><a href="#git-yilia主题" class="headerlink" title="git yilia主题"></a><strong>git yilia主题</strong></h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">clone</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git</span> <span class="string">themes/yilia</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在<code>blog/_config.yml</code>中加入<code>themes</code>信息和<code>github库</code>信息</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/heroamd/heroamd.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在<code>blog\source</code>加入<code>CNAME</code>文件以改变域名，这个路径里面的所有文件都将会生成并放置在网站的根目录下。</p>
<p>tips:<strong>所有代码前面不能加空格~~</strong></p>
<h3 id="生成SSH添加到GitHub"><a href="#生成SSH添加到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="生成SSH添加到GitHub"></a><strong>生成SSH添加到GitHub</strong></h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">config</span> <span class="string">--global</span> <span class="string">user.name</span> <span class="string">"heroamd"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">git</span> <span class="string">config</span> <span class="string">--global</span> <span class="string">user.email</span> <span class="string">"icenet11@163.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="检查是否正确"><a href="#检查是否正确" class="headerlink" title="检查是否正确"></a><strong>检查是否正确</strong></h3><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config user.email</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="配置ssh"><a href="#配置ssh" class="headerlink" title="配置ssh"></a><strong>配置ssh</strong></h3><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"icenet11@163.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="连接一下服务器测试是否成功"><a href="#连接一下服务器测试是否成功" class="headerlink" title="连接一下服务器测试是否成功"></a><strong>连接一下服务器测试是否成功</strong></h3><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="如果提示"><a href="#如果提示" class="headerlink" title="如果提示"></a><strong>如果提示</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hi heroamd! You&#39;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="表示成功！！"><a href="#表示成功！！" class="headerlink" title="表示成功！！"></a>表示成功！！</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="添加Github的ip记录"><a href="#添加Github的ip记录" class="headerlink" title="添加Github的ip记录"></a><strong>添加Github的ip记录</strong></h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">185.199.108.153</span><br><span class="line">185.199.109.153</span><br><span class="line">185.199.110.153</span><br><span class="line">185.199.111.153</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="备份一下本电脑的代理端口排除的目录"><a href="#备份一下本电脑的代理端口排除的目录" class="headerlink" title="备份一下本电脑的代理端口排除的目录"></a>备份一下本电脑的代理端口排除的目录</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">localhost;127.*;10.*;172.16.*;172.17.*;172.18.*;172.19.*;172.20.*;172.21.*;172.22.*;172.23.*;172.24.*;172.25.*;172.26.*;172.27.*;172.28.*;172.29.*;172.30.*;172.31.*;192.168.*;windows10.microdone.cn</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="修改图片和头像"><a href="#修改图片和头像" class="headerlink" title="修改图片和头像"></a><strong>修改图片和头像</strong></h1><p> <code>themes/yilia/source/</code>下，可添加一个 <code>assets</code> 文件夹，里面存放图片资源即可</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 微信二维码图片</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">weixin:</span>  <span class="string">/assets/wechat.png</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 头像图片</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar:</span>  <span class="string">/assets/head.jpg</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 网页图标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">favicon:</span>  <span class="string">/assets/head.jpg</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="所有文章模块的更改"><a href="#所有文章模块的更改" class="headerlink" title="所有文章模块的更改"></a>所有文章模块的更改</h1><p> 1、请确保node版本大于6.2<br>  2、在博客根目录（注意不是yilia根目录）执行以下命令：<br>  <code>npm i hexo-generator-json-content --save</code></p>
<p> 3、在根目录_config.yml里添加配置：</p>
 <figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">jsonContent:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">meta:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">pages:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">posts:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">text:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">raw:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">content:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">slug:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">updated:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">comments:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">link:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">excerpt:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>tips: 注意空格</p>
]]></content>
